ayalathe adheham ( malayalam : അയലത തെ അദ ദേഹം ) is a 1992 suspense malayalam film directed by rajasenan and written by sasidharan arattuvazhi .   it stars jayaram , gautami , siddique , vaishnavi , meena , and thilakan .   the songs were composed by perumbavoor g. raveendranath , with the film score by mohan sithara .